Package org.transitime.ipc.clients

Contains the client side code for connecting to an RMI interface in order to read configuration, predictions, or vehicle data from the server.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgencyMonitorClient
    Makes the ServerStatusInterface.monitor() RMI call easy to access.
    CommandsInterfaceFactory
    Provides a CommandsInterface client that can be sent commands.
    ConfigInterfaceFactory
    Provides a ConfigInterface client that can be queried for configuration info.
    PredictionsInterfaceFactory
    Provides a PredictionsInterface client that can be queried for predictions.
    ServerStatusInterfaceFactory
    Provides a ServerStatusInterface client that can be queried for server status info via IPC.
    VehiclesInterfaceFactory
    Provides a VehiclesInterface client that can be queried for Vehicle info.

Package org.transitime.ipc.clients Description

Contains the client side code for connecting to an RMI interface in order to read configuration, predictions, or vehicle data from the server.
